				<h1>Coding Standards</h1>
        <p>
          These can be found <a href="http://wiki.transformativeworks.org/mediawiki/Coding_Standards:_XHTML/CSS">at the OTW internal wiki</a>.
        </p>
        <h3>HTML Inviolable Rules</h3>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>All tags must be closed</strong></li>
          <li>All markup must be valid and well-formed.</li>
          <li>Tables are only for tabular data: three or more pieces of information that can be cross referenced in a matrix.</li>
          <li>All markup must degrade gracefully.</li>
        </ol>
        <h3>CSS Inviolable Rules</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>All classes must be single common English words (no-hyphenation-please)</li>
          <li>No CSS3 for critical display.</li>
          <li>All styles must degrade gracefully.</li>
        </ol>
